	<div class="grid-article-bd">
		<h1 class="smart-dotdotdot">乐视体育也要做电竞，但它的竞争对手都来头不小</h1>
	</div>
	<div class="grid-article-ft  clearfix">
		<span class="smart-date" data-originDate="2016-05-23 12:37:57 +0800"></span>
		<div class="ribbon">
				<span class="iconfont icon-message">2</span>
				<span class="iconfont icon-heart">4</span>
		</div>
	</div>
</a>

                    </div>
                    <div class="packery-item article">
                        <!-- 普通文章格子，占位1x1，智能占位 -->
